**Set these Postman environment variables:**

- `base_url`: `http://localhost:8000`
- `access_token`: (set automatically after login via Tests script)
- `refresh_token`: (set automatically after login via Tests script)

**Auto-set tokens with this Login Tests script:**

```javascript
const json = pm.response.json();
if (json.data && json.data.access) {
    pm.environment.set("access_token", json.data.access);
    pm.environment.set("refresh_token", json.data.refresh);
}
```

**Register Tests script:**
```javascript
const json = pm.response.json();
if (json.data && json.data.tokens) {
    pm.environment.set("access_token", json.data.tokens.access);
    pm.environment.set("refresh_token", json.data.tokens.refresh);
}
```
